Author: HU_ME
Title: ✅✅[ANN][ICO]✅HUYUcoin✅DECENTRALIZED GENEALOGY POWERED BY BLOCKCHAIN✅✅
Body: Thank you for your question.  We have a roadmap for the overall HUYU product which includes HUYUcoin as a utility token for use on the huyu.co site. The huyu.co site is independent of cryptos and is a platform that will be widely used as it will have uptake from a broad user base. The growth mechanism within the platform is an intelligent family tree that will appeal to both young and old. The product is fun and very easy to use.  The majority of the huyu.co site will be free, however should a user wish to use some of the advanced features then HUYUcoin will be required to activate these.  The income generated on the site will come from outside the crypto market whilst still keeping the site AD-FREE. This income will be generated by normal business activities and ensure a constant drip of fiat into the HUYU ecosystem.  The MACRO reporting data will be extremely useful to market, trend and census research. This too will need to be paid for using HUYUcoin. (Please note reporting is only ever done on a MACRO level and never an individual level. The method used to construct the two modules will make sure of this.)  As modules are introduced to the huyu.co site HUYUcoin will become more and more useful. We have a development roadmap which will see new features and modules added to the platform regularly (monthly). All of these have been conceptualized and specified.  A successful ICO will fast track the development of these modules, however the success of the site huyu.co is not dependent on the ICO. We have raised enough funding privately to complete development of the MVP and launch by 1 September 2018.  The adoption and use of HUYUcoin on the huyu.co is unavoidable and since we are extremely confident that huyu.co will be a success, it follows that HUYUcoin will become more and more useful.

Author: HU_ME
Title: ✅✅[ANN][ICO]✅HUYUcoin✅DECENTRALIZED GENEALOGY POWERED BY BLOCKCHAIN✅✅
Body: Hi. We have been working on this project for a long time and are confident we can attract at least that many users in the first 3 months. We know that 2mil in 90 days is a lot but we are confident in the virality of the product as it is simple, easy to use and fun.  We are not expecting users to use the product on a daily basis just to sign up and start the process of building their own family tree. The system will then match them with their current family that are already on the system (whether they are registered users or not). We do not need a person to be a user to be found. The goal is to make the definitive family tree for all.  The product is free to use and will allow users the claim their place in a global family tree that will hopefully be around for a very long time if not forever.  In time the features on the site will grow and users will engage more and more with each other thereby increasing the accuracy of the family tree data and recording their own lives for future generations to look back on.  The project is now in the final phases of development and will be uploaded for beta testing during June. Final bug testing on the beta will take place during July and August ready for launch on 1 September 2018.

Author: HU_ME
Title: ✅✅[ANN][ICO]✅HUYUcoin✅DECENTRALIZED GENEALOGY POWERED BY BLOCKCHAIN✅✅
Body: Hi, thank you for the question.  The virality engine built into the family tree module of the site will use information uploaded by the users themselves to intuitively connect family. We do not need a person to register as a user to appear on the system. We are not using current database information such as birth certificates etc... to find people (although there will be a place to store this information), the system will do this through a relational database. The technology we are using has been tested in other environments which have been using it very successfully to make relational connections.  If you as a user input your family tree the system will help you fill the gaps in your data, and show you family connections that you might not be aware of. This might not happen instantly, but it will happen as more and more users input their data. The system will also actively try match unregistered nodes on your tree with registered users. So as your family register accounts your tree will come to life.  The benefits of the system will not be seen instantly it will be something that will grow and become more and more useful as time goes on. The same goes for the lost relatives. It will take some time to gather  the information required for this. However, with the help of the algorithms we have written for this module we are confident that this type of information will become available and will be accurate. The system constantly cross checks the input data from users to determine what is correct and what is false.  This is a long haul project (started in 2014) with some extremely aspirational goals, but we are certain it will succeed.  Some of the ideas we are offering are not new, some are, but we are confident that the way in which it has been stitched together is a world first.

Author: HU_ME
Title: ✅✅[ANN][ICO]✅HUYUcoin✅DECENTRALIZED GENEALOGY POWERED BY BLOCKCHAIN✅✅
Body: Free ancestry, for everyone, forever  HUYU is a free ancestry platform that will allow a user to connect and interact with family and friends globally. The content on HUYU will be generated by the users themselves and the platform will be ad-free.  Families are the foundation of human relationships. The intelligent genealogy engine will allow users to connect with family quickly and easily. HUYU will strengthen these relationships in a secure manner. The benefits of this are convenient and secure family communication, global gifting, secure photo and contact sharing.  HUYU will allow children to have social media accounts as their identity will be confirmed by a responsible parent or guardian. HUYU will allow the guardian to monitor traffic, restrict contacts and instill good online and social media habits in those that they are responsible for.  The addition of friends in time will complete “Your World”. Global gifting made easy  Giving a gift to a family member in another country or territory has always been a challenge and expensive. There is freight to consider, as well as import duties and the enforce ability of warranties in a foreign jurisdiction. The HUYU WISHLIST will relieve the user of these challenges. The WISHLIST will work on any online store and will ensure that users receive a gift they want. Satisfied customers - all around!   How long do we wait for HUYU to launch?  HUYU is currently less than 6 months from worldwide launch. From conceptualization in 2014 the team produced a high-level prototype which has proven that the concept is achievable. The company HUYU SA Pty (Ltd) was registered in 2015 and work began almost immediately. Towards the end of 2016 a major breakthrough was made with the family tree with regards to the mechanics of how it builds. We feel this will be incredibly disruptive as the tree is now intelligent and will not require a curator to verify the data. Data with be verified over and over again by the users themselves, on the fly. The framework, databases and 90% of the front-end for the final product have been completed. This final product will be released to the public in September 2018 and is expected to attract at least 2 mil users within the first 90 days.   The Perpetual Life Cycle of HUYUcoin  The value of the HUYUcoin will be determined by scarcity. 650 million coins will be released during the ICO. As the MACRO data grows more and more reports will be run, hence more HUYUcoin will be needed. HUYUcoin will also be used for other features on the site huyu.co such as partner incentives and using additional HUYU services. Basic genealogy, communication and storage will always be free thus ensuring the user's legacy in posterity. The site will be AD-FREE!!  Through the vehicle of supply and demand, users will be able to determine the value of their MACRO data for themselves. HUYU will release all coins used and will not HODL. This will ensure the supply of HUYUcoin in the market place remains constant and the FREE market will determine the value, not HUYU.  Personal user data will be kept safe through the employment of decentralization. Only MACRO data will be used in the reporting tools. This data will be extracted from the decentralized network on a macro level to a separate network of query servers that will deliver the reports requested by data buyers. These buyers will need to pay for the results with HUYUcoin they have purchased on the open market.   Pre-sale & ICO  The pre-sale of HUYUcoin is underway currently and will end on 20 May 2018 @ 23:00 GMT. 50 million HUYUcoin is available on the Waves Platform as a HUYU/BTC pairing.  The first stage of the public ICO will begin 1 June 2018 @ 0:00 GMT.  First Stage 200 million HUYUcoin will be available @ 30% discount (263 Satoshi each) Second Stage 200 million HUYUcoin @ 15% discount (319 Satoshi each) Third Stage 200 million HUYUcoin @ 375 Satoshi each  EACH STAGE WILL FOLLOW DIRECTLY AFTER THE ONE BEFORE.     How will HUYU use the funds?  The funds raised in the ICO will ensure a runway of 3-5 years for the project. This will be more than sufficient time for HUYU to build the data required for the services on the platform.  These funds will allow HUYU to continue with development of future modules that have been conceptualized and specified.  The viral genealogy module will attract over 2 million users within 90 days of launch. This will form the launch pad from which HUYU will expand.  The funds will be utilized as follows:   Why Waves Platform?  WAVES has been chosen as the preferred platform to launch the HUYUcoin for various reasons.  ●   As a truly decentralized exchange WAVES is less likely to be influenced by policy decisions made by central banks and governments. Decentralization will allow for the highest degree of security and reliability. ●   Ultra-low cost of transactions giving the user maximum value. ●   Fast - with the introduction of WAVES NG the network can now process up to 100 transactions / second. This will be increased to 1000 transactions / second once the full upgrade is implemented. ●   WAVES has multiple FIAT gateways allowing users to easily convert FIAT into crypto. ●   Scalable, the WAVES platform and trading DEX are fully scalable to manage higher future volumes. ●   Simple and easy to use interface - WAVES has gone to great lengths to make the interface resemble the standards expected and seen in online banking applications.
